        """
        CREATE (:TestNode)
        """
    When executing query:
        """
        MATCH (t:TestNode)
        OPTIONAL MATCH (t)-[:LINKED]-(a:AnotherNode)
        RETURN t, SUM(CASE WHEN NOT EXISTS(a.Status) OR COALESCE(a.Status, 'Complete') <> 'Complete' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS PendingCount
        """
    Then the result should be:
      | t           | PendingCount |
      | (:TestNode) | 0            |
    And no side effects

